params.amounts: The amount to stake for each route
params.routes: Routes to stake funds to e.g. [(ETH, PLG), (ETH, AVAX)]
params.token: The token to stake (zero for native coin)

stake((uint8,uint8)[],uint256[],address).notice: Any relayer can add stake to take swap requests & earn fees;the stake is bound to one route, which consist of source & destination networks (stake amounts must be identical)
